rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Right now we discussing among selves
about how to obtain merchandise
cheaper and lower prices.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0002
rows.name:
We think long and hard about how
to help poor people living in Torika
Alley...

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Only conclusion we come to so far is
to boost economy.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If everyone buy lots of products from
us, that mean more demand.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Which mean in turn we get to produce
more, and price of goods go down.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Purchase of more products help
develop country, and as country
develop, commodities get cheaper!
